Description: Provides common base-level functions for undertaking epiphytotic
    modelling and simulation studies in R. Included are tools for modelling the
    spatial movement of splash and wind dispersed plant disease inoculum,
    estimating disease progress, and formatting and imputing weather data for
    use in process-based plant disease models.
